spec_data.Name: libmudflap-devel
spec_data.License: GPLv3+ and GPLv3+ with exceptions and GPLv2+ with exceptions and LGPLv2+ and BSD
spec_data.Description:
This package contains headers for building mudflap-instrumented programs.

To instrument a non-threaded program, add -fmudflap
option to GCC and when linking add -lmudflap, for threaded programs
also add -fmudflapth and -lmudflapth.
